          <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
            <text>Heading to <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM351466">section 36</extref></citation>: omit <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">court-martial</emphasis></amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">Court Martial</emphasis></amend.in>.</text>
